# Moodify Configuration (All Optional!)
# =====================================
#
# Moodify works out-of-the-box without any configuration.
# These settings are only for advanced users who want customization.

# OPTIONAL: Custom Spotify Client ID
# Only needed if you want to use your own Spotify app instead of the shared one
# Get your Client ID from: https://developer.spotify.com/dashboard
# SPOTIFY_CLIENT_ID=your_spotify_client_id_here

# OPTIONAL: OpenAI API Key for enhanced natural language processing
# Get your API key from: https://platform.openai.com/api-keys
# If not set, the app uses a built-in keyword-based parser (works great!)
# OPENAI_API_KEY=your_openai_api_key_here

# Quick Start (No Configuration Needed):
# ======================================
# 1. Just run: ./moodify login
# 2. Start searching: ./moodify search happy upbeat songs
#
# Advanced Setup (Optional):
# ==========================
# 1. Copy this file: cp .env.example .env
# 2. Uncomment and set the values you want to customize
# 3. Source the file: source .env
# 4. Run: ./moodify login
